{"tid":2033604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝手足 哭𠹌咗","createTime":"2020-05-24T18:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T18:17:41.000Z","uid":313482,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9188a562f4abc3cc4f1f6c468014d851c1722697","tid":2033604,"uid":313482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:11:42.000Z","msg":"話說件事係咁 <br />\n今日我去咗間黃店麵舖食野 <br />\n我自己一個人食 <br />\n排隊嗰陣 入面有兩個位 <br />\n而企我後面個男人都係一個人 <br />\n就順理成章咁一齊坐 <br />\n個店員以為我地兩個係識得 <br />\n就連同枱都係 <br />\n因為同一時間落單 所以兩個張單合埋咗一張單 咁我嗰陣心諗 食完比番錢咪得囉  但食完我比錢佢 佢竟然唔要  同我講請我食 咁我當然話唔好 我話比返錢佢 佢話唔要 就好快就走咗  我嗰陣o咗嘴 <br />\n想同佢講番聲多謝哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望你安全返到去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793e4a5c3b8f83fd0b67e30986467c7fce47055d","tid":2033604,"uid":36566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:13:47.000Z","msg":"人間有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed3b7819d824bc1bcc7e3c71ac14c59bd93363b","tid":2033604,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkg